page.title: 04FARMING
page.content: In the countryside are woods and fields.The fields are owned by different farmers,the woods are mixed of coniferous and deciduous trees. There are dog roses growing wild with other undergrowth.There is no decent track or path leading deeper into the woods except for tractor tracks. There are also wild cherries growing amongst the undergrowth.The fields in the countryside contain crops such as broad beans,rape,wheat,peas and barley .Some fields are used for grazing.
